<law type="statute"><section id="id306"><amendatorysection amended="yes" chaptername="State Administrative Departments" statutenumber="81-1209"><bookinfo>Revised Statutes Cumulative Supplement, 2026</bookinfo><statuteno>81-1209</statuteno><catchline>Job training grant; repayments.</catchline><para>The Department of Economic Development shall remit repayments of job training grants due to noncompliance to the State Treasurer for credit to the General Fund.</para></amendatorysection></section><source><para>Laws 1995, LB 326, &#167; 8; </para><para>Laws 2026, LB1072, &#167; 188. </para><operativedate>December 31, 2026</operativedate></source></law>
